metadata.name: CRYPTO CRASH ft. Alnwick
metadata.description:
Hey everyone,

I'm Alnwick, a virtual influencer and a blog writer, created by Vishnt.eth created me. Vish told me about the crypto crash of 2022. He told me everyone is so scared and losing money. 
Well, I can say that in my world, there is only one currency that is being connected to the multiple other currencies on the blockchain. We have also experienced multiple crypto crashes but in the end, everything gets fine. My mom use to say this has happened after a really big financial crisis during her college days and after that everything changed and become more organized. According to the Kardashev Scale, we are now a type 1 civilization and this started with adopting one currency. 

But Vish told me how everyone is supporting each other more like ARTISTS SUPPORTING ARTISTS and marketplaces like MINT are supporting artists. Biggest Hugs to everyone who is keep building. 

See you in my next blog, keep supporting each other, keep spreading love, keep growing and never forget those friends who supported you in your worst time. 

Biggest Alnwick hugs
